<h2 id="showing-the-code-on-checkout">Showing the Code on Checkout <a class="headerlink" href="validating-coupons#showing-the-code-on-checkout" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Refresh and re-POST the form! Coupon applied! Except... I don't see <em>any</em> difference:
the total is <em>still</em> $99.</p>
<p>Here's why: it's specific to our <code>ShoppingCart</code> object. In <code>checkout.html.twig</code>,
we print <code>cart.total</code>:</p>
