<p>But, <em>this</em> method doesn't subtract the coupon discount. I did this to keep things
clean: total is really more like a "sub-total".</p>
<p>But no worries, the method below this - <code>getTotalWithDiscount()</code> - subtracts the
coupon code:</p>
